be used for optical\nidentification of galaxy groups down to eROSITA's mass detection limits of\n$10^{13} M_\\odot$, as well as the detection of the largest filaments for\npioneering studies of their X-ray emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2019 16:10:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Apr 2019 11:45:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-02"}
