 show that $\\delta_{\\mathrm{weak}}=1$ for the i.i.d. Gaussian model.\n  (2) The optimal design for the spectral method coincides with that for the\ni.i.d. Gaussian model, where the latter was recently introduced by Luo,\nAlghamdi and Lu.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2019 17:26:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2020 09:57:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-10"}
