esence of symmetry that reverses the space-time orientation, we classify all\npossible topological crystalline insulators whose vortex defect carries a\nfractional charge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Mar 2019 06:00:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Apr 2019 03:57:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2020 15:35:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-12"}
