ngs\nfor our point cloud sparsification method both on unperturbed as well as noisy\n3D point cloud data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Mar 2019 12:03:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Mar 2019 12:14:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 30 Sep 2019 10:01:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-01"}
